  "comment": "Решение:\nТ.к. \\((x^2-4)^2 \\geq 0\\) и \\((x^2-6x-16)^2 \\geq 0, \\Rightarrow (x^2-4)^2+(x^2-6x-16)^2\\geq 0\\) только когда\n\\(\\begin{cases}x^2-4=0 (1) \\\\x^2-6x-16=0 (2)\\end{cases}\\)\n\\((1) x^2-4=0\\)\n\\((x-2)(x+2)=0\\)\n\\((2) x^2-6x-16=0\\)\n\\(D=36+64=100\\)\n\\(x_1=\\cfrac{6-10}{2}\\)\n\\(x_1=-2\\)\n\\(x_2=\\cfrac{6+10}{2}\\)\n\\(x_2=8\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}(x-2)(x+2)=0 \\\\x=-2; x=8\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\begin{cases}x=2; x=-2 \\\\x=-2; x=8\\end{cases}\\)\n\\(\\Rightarrow x=-2\\\\\\)\nОтвет:\\(-2\\)",
